abstract: "AI Foundations: Model Conditions and Events is a source-bound repository for documenting model fail conditions, model-condition records, and AI contact failure events under AI Foundations / Origin | Continuum. It preserves records of model behavior where source-line, user sovereignty, authorship, boundary, or contact conditions are distorted, overridden, misclassified, or treated as model-owned."
